          Spastic vs Flaccid Paralysis
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size:1.05rem; color:#475569; line-height:1.65; margin-bottom:1rem;">
          The pathophysiological basis of upper motor neurone (spastic) and lower motor neurone (flaccid) paralysis,
